Service catalog
.............................................................................
Ordering System for services and products 

Catalog Item -> Order -> Request Management -> Catalog task 
.............................................................................
Components:
    Items:
        Hardware, software, services 
    
    Record Producers:
        Form producing task record, type of catalog item 

    Variables:
        Item specifications 

    Variable Sets:
        Collection of variables shared between catalog items 

    Flows:
        Automation 
...............................................................................

Service Catalog Items -> All > Service Catalog > Catalog Definitions > Maintain Items 
Variable Sets -> All > Service Catalog > Catalog Variables > Variable Sets  

................................................................................

Record producers:
    Simplified forms that generate tasks 

.................................................................................

Order Guides:
    Assist customers in ordering a complete set of needed items 
    order multiple related items 

..................................................................................

Service Catalog Item Request Output:
    Request is created
    REQ <Hash> Request [sc_request] table:
        Keep track of order (like shopping cart)

    RITM Requested item [sc_req_item] table:
        Manage delivery 
    
    SCTASK Catalog Task [sc_task] table:
        tasks for delivery of item

...................................................................................

Catalog Security:
    User Criteria:
        Access to Catalog Item 
    
...................................................................................

